objectType: Sword (hilt and two pieces of blade)
description: The hilt is beautifully ornamented with spirals and lines. The butt is also ornamented and a ped projects from it. The hilt is in fine condition, but the two pieces of the blade are much chipped. There is a piece missing near the hilt. The blade has a strong rib. The blade has been made separately from the hilt, and slipped into a groove, where it is secured with four rivets.
